USB wifi on this machine -
Go to Desktop/install/usbwifi
# Do a sudo install
# If you uncompress the tar folder you might end up undoing some of the local changes to get it compiling.
# So, uncompress onnly once. I have commented out the uncompress part in the install file. 
# If you get a fresh copy from the disc you migh end up doing it again
sudo ./install


